text: Dionisis Angelopoulos (born 5 August 1992) is a Greek rower. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's coxless four. The Greek team finished in 8th place. == References == Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Greek male rowers Category:Rowers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic rowers of Greece Category:Greek sportspeople stubs Category:Mediterranean Games silver medalists for Greece Category:Mediterranean Games medalists in rowing Category:Competitors at the 2013 Mediterranean Games
